data.title: 971: Correspondence related to visit of Sir Alec …
data.meta_description: FCO 24/971: Correspondence related to visit of Sir Alec Douglas-Home, Secretary of  State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, to United Nations General  …
data.text:
Scope and Content:

Record contains notes that several of the Asean foreign ministers, including Rajaratnam will be in New York at the same time and it is suggested that Sir Alec should meet with them to discuss the progress being made towards the Five Power Defence Arrangment
